name: CLSErrorUserInfoKey
desc: Keys that appear in the user info dictionary in errors that ClassKit creates.

items.name: static let objectKey: CLSErrorUserInfoKey
items.desc: A key whose value is the object that caused the error.

items.name: static let underlyingErrorsKey: CLSErrorUserInfoKey
items.desc: A key whose value is the array of errors that contributed to this error.
